Some months ago, it came to the attention of a [[white_knight|concerned citizen]] that 12chan had stepped up its operation from merely importing pictures of Eastern European loli, to producing them - but with white American girls, thanks to a nefarious agent on the inside... That agent was none other than 12chan hero and pedo-scum, 38-year-old '''Bradley Dayley''' of Elk Grove, CA! Mr. Dayley was charged with sexually molesting a 12-year-old female relative over a three year period and, additionally, an 18-year-old girl who was [[sixteen_year_old_girl|sixteen]] at the time. 

Being a [[pretty cool guy]], Mr. Dayley was found in possession of a hoarder's amount of pornographic pictures and videotapes: all evidence used later to send him to the [[ass_rape|Irony]] [[jail|Hole]]. The exact same content was also found on the front page of the [[Obvious|JB section]] of the [[12chan|Internet Hellfire Club]]. But, much to the chagrin of the [[pedo|average user]], not uploaded was Mr. Dayley's private stash - his famed [[rape|penetration pics]] and [[bukkake|'''a legendary cumshot''']], where his load was reportedly seen around the young girls ass.<br> 
But even before these files existed, there was a link posted on his daughter, Jessie's, [[Stickam|Stickam account]]: a secret path for cool kids, which led to tantalizing, and frequently updated [[CP|"request-pics"]] that Dayley himself took and uploaded. With no father to get in the way ([[Incest|except during a threesome]]), "Jessie" and her sister became [[e-famous]] - like sexual genies - instantly, for their youth and their [[rape|willingness]] to pose for pictures and requests. Such was their fame, that the "Jessie/Brianna" thread was stuck at the forefront of ''/jb/'' and protected by the [[Sick Fuck|mods]].

